  "name": "Morrison CFD Hemolysis Credibility Assessment — CPB Worst-Case Operating Conditions (MRL 2)",
  "description": "Credibility evidence package for CFD-based hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass conditions. The model is intended to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. All seven assessed credibility factors meet required gradation levels; six factors are scoped out as acceptable at MRL 2. Decision: Accepted for intended regulatory submission.",
