      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, formal iterative convergence quantification beyond residual monitoring is not required; standard residual convergence to 1e-5 is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Solver residuals were monitored to 1e-5 for all equations. No additional iterative error quantification was performed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping. Factor is not assessed beyond baseline monitoring."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
