      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2, a qualitative assessment of the equivalency between validation test inputs and clinical use inputs is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "A qualitative review confirmed that the validation test inputs (fluid properties, flow rates, rotational speeds) are representative of the CPB clinical operating envelope. Formal quantitative equivalency analysis was not performed, consistent with MRL 2 scoping."
