    "rationale": "All seven credibility factors assessed for MRL 2 meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The six factors not assessed are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40-2018 MRL 2 requirements. The CFD model is accepted as providing sufficient credibility evidence to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump in the CPB indication. The submission package is approved for regulatory use.",
